ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS (UKKUSIKSALIK NATIONAL PARK, NUNAVUT) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of some 20,558 square kilometres of land in order to establish Ukkusiksalik National Park in Nunavut (formerly called Wager Bay National Park).
